    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2004 Porsche 911 Turbo is a mechanically sound example featuring the iconic 3.6L Mezger flat-six engine. Power is delivered via a Getrag G96/50 6-speed manual transaxle and a permanent all-wheel-drive system. To address platform-specific longevity, the coolant lines have been pinned, and the hydraulic clutch slave cylinder was recently replaced. The twin K16 turbochargers provide consistent boost pressure across the rev range. The suspension has been enhanced with Bilstein PSS10 adjustable coilovers, offering superior damping and cornering poise. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the drivetrain integrity is excellent, with consistent compression across all cylinders and a leak-free undercarriage. A turn-key performance machine for the discerning driver.",
      "price": 38500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
